// Blaze — Mage fire DoT.
//
// Applied by fire abilities (Fireblast, Flamestrike, Flamewrath).
// Removed by frost damage — any DamageEvent with a Frost tag on a blazing target
// removes blaze (handled by status/systems/cross_interact.rs reading removed_by_tags).
//
// tick_interval: 1.0 second; on_tick fires DamageEvent with Fire tag.
// The Fire tag on the tick means: if the target also has Frostbite, the tick will
// trigger frostbite removal (cross_interact reads frostbite's removed_by_tags: [Fire]).
// This is emergent from the system — no special case needed here.
(
    id: "blaze",
    display_name: "Blaze",
    stacking: RefreshOnReapply,
    base_duration_secs: 4.0,
    tick_interval_secs: Some(1.0),
    on_apply_hooks: ["blaze_apply"],     // sets enemy visuals
    on_tick_hooks: ["blaze_tick_damage"],
    on_remove_hooks: [],
    removed_by_tags: [Frost],
    removes_on_apply: [],
)
